en_384601_0	An eye-clinic for benefit of Ingiriya civilians was conducted by the 582 Brigade troops on Sunday (11) on the directions of Major General Sathyapriya Liyanage, Commander, Security Forces - West and under the supervision of 582 Brigade Commander.
en_384601_1	It took place at Ingiriya Divisional Secretariat.
en_384601_2	More than 150 civilians attended it for treatment.
en_384601_3	The Elvitigala Lions Club in cooperation with the Army launched it.
en_384601_4	582 Brigade Commander, Brigadier S.M.S.P.B Samarakoon arranged all requirements with his Brigade troops.
